---
description: "Requires canonical field order and keywords in topology.yml. Applies to any *.yml under examples/, lib/, src/."
globs: "**/topology.yml"
alwaysApply: true
---
- Field order must be: name, routes, events, functions, mutations, queues, channels, states, pages
- Recognize trigger phrases: 'add function', 'add event', 'new mutation', 'define page', 'add channel', 'entity', 'component'
- Warn on attributes not matching known spec.
